                    currentModel: "Nucleus contains protons and neutrons (nucleons); electrons occupy probabilistic orbitals",
                    scale: "Atom diameter ≈ 10⁻¹⁰ m; nucleus diameter ≈ 10⁻¹⁵ m (100 000 times smaller)"
