                    analogy: "EMF is like the wage paid to a worker (energy in); PD across a component is like money spent at different shops (energy out); internal resistance is like a compulsory deduction (energy lost internally)",
                    mathematicalRelation: "ε = V_terminal + V_internal = V + Ir",
                    openCircuit: "No current flows → no voltage drop across internal resistance → V_terminal = ε",
